Ridge Regression

library(MASS)
m<-lm.ridge(y ~ .,data=growth,lambda=seq(0,0.1,0.0001))
#选择最佳lambda
select(m)
## modified HKB estimator is 1.430689 
## modified L-W estimator is 3.907841 
## smallest value of GCV  at 0.1
#根据最小GCV设定lambda
s<-m$lambda[which.min(m$GCV)]
#用设定的lambda岭回归
r1<-lm.ridge(y ~ .,data=growth,lambda=s)
r1

lars包-lar模型(Least Angle Regression)

  • for linear regression (not for logit)
  • can do stepwise and cv
  • can do ridge and cv
  • can do lasso and cv
